title: Penny Skateboards at Volcom TCT - Cardiff
description:
We headed over to Seaside Reef in Cardiff, CA for the first TCT stop of 2015, to have some fun in the sun on Penny's and watch the surfers do their thing. 

The TCT is a grassroots surf contest that Volcom puts on globally every year. Penny Skateboards is proud to be a sponsor of the regional event in the USA.
